copr-some-nice-fonts
====================

This is a Fedora/CentOS repo for easy installing of some nice fonts. This
includes the following fonts:

- Arial
- Comic Sans Ms
- Courier New
- Georgia
- Helvetica Neue
- Helvetica
- Lucida Sans Unicode
- Tahoma
- Times New Roman
- Trebuchet Ms
- Verdana

Building
--------

cp *.ttf ~/rpmbuild/SOURCES && rpmbuild -ba some-nice-fonts.spec
